<abstract><t>DNSSEC provides data integrity and authentication for DNSSEC validators.  However, without valid trust anchor(s) and an acceptable value for the current time, DNSSEC validation cannot be performed. This document lists the requirements to be addressed so resolvers can have DNSSEC validation can be always-on.</t></abstract>

